snippet.title: Free Post-Launch and Endgame Trailer | Rainbow Six Extraction
snippet.description:
Rainbow Six Extraction has an entirely free post-launch program with limited-time events and new content.
Maelstrom Protocol, a challenging endgame mode for skilled players, will be available at Launch. 

Tom Clancy's Rainbow Six Extraction will be available on 20th January 2022 on PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, Xbox Series X | S, Xbox One, Stadia and PC.
For more info: 
www.rainbowsixextraction.com
